{
  "stem": "27509.7",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But that was the interaction.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And it was of, course, it was an unequal relationship in terms that they were settled and well-to-do.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we were to some extent at the mercy of circumstances and their good will, to the extent to which they were ready to to help us, and so on.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we e existed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Somehow other people existed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Some found work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Some did this.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Some did that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I don't think people really went hungry.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Somehow-- somehow, they managed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "You know, and in normal circumstances how we're all equal in our traditions of life and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] all in the same homes, and so it's individual.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Some manage better, some [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But as I said before, the people least-- least educated were the ones who adjusted first, precisely because they had no inhibitions.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They didn't have to consider how far down they were from what they were previously.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They had nothing, and they came with nothing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And every opportunity was an appropriate opportunity for them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they grabbed it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they were-- precisely because they didn't have those inhibitions-- that I was yesterday a owner of a big plant and a big enterprise and so on, and employed 200 people or 500 people-- they did-- they did business and were happy with their lot and made Shabbat for themselves.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the strongest images that I've brought, they were mixed-- it was a mixture of those contrasts.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And of course, there was always that element of knowing and realizing that I've got a family somewhere in-- in-- in Kazakhstan.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
